quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  101,1,The Striking Disaster
  101,2,What is the Striking Disaster
  101,3,And what will make you realize what the Striking Disaster is
  101,4,˹It is˺ the Day people will be like scattered moths
  101,5,and the mountains will be like carded wool
  101,6,So as for those whose scale is heavy ˹with good deeds˺
  101,7,they will be in a life of bliss
  101,8,And as for those whose scale is light
  101,9,their home will be the abyss
  101,10,And what will make you realize what that is
  101,11,˹It is˺ a scorching Fire